the awards. Sweet pickles.

761
00:53:03,263 --> 00:53:08,936
First prize to Mrs. Edwin
Metcalfe of Pottsville.

762
00:53:15,526 --> 00:53:19,278
Second prize to...

763
00:53:19,279 --> 00:53:21,572
To Mrs. Agnes Field

764
00:53:21,573 --> 00:53:23,867
