only one thing left for this man,

856
00:59:07,002 --> 00:59:08,294
the river.

857
00:59:09,254 --> 00:59:13,090
On the other hand, if somebody was to
get a great artist like Emily Edwards

858
00:59:13,091 --> 00:59:15,676
